'''佐治亚南方大学'''（{{lang-en|Georgia Southern University}}）是一所坐落于[[美国|美国]][[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]][[斯泰茨伯勒_(佐治亚州)|斯泰茨伯勒]]市的公立学校<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usg.edu/inst/profile/georgia_southern_university | title=佐治亚南方大学 | publisher=佐治亚大学系统 | accessdate=2015年2月12日 | archive-date=2015年3月27日 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327154017/http://www.usg.edu/inst/profile/georgia_southern_university | dead-url=no }}</ref>，
始建于1906年，
校园面积900英亩（3.6平方千米）。
该校为佐治亚大学系统中之一员，
亦是佐治亚州南部最大之高等教育中心。

佐治亚南方大学被卡耐基高等教育机构分类评为博士研究型大学<ref>{{cite web | url=http://carnegieclassifications.iu.edu/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=139931&start_page=institution.php&clq=%7B%22ipug2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ipgrad2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22enrprofile2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ugprfile2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22sizeset2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22basic2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22eng2005_ids%22%3A%22%22%2C%22search_string%22%3A%22georgia+southern+university%22%2C%22level%22%3A%22%22%2C%22control%22%3A%22%22%2C%22accred%22%3A%22%22%2C%22state%22%3A%22%22%2C%22region%22%3A%22%22%2C%22urbanicity%22%3A%22%22%2C%22womens%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hbcu%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hsi%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tribal%22%3A%22%22%2C%22msi%22%3A%22%22%2C%22landgrant%22%3A%22%22%2C%22coplac%22%3A%22%22%2C%22urban%22%3A%22%22%7D | title=佐治亚南方大学 | publisher=卡耐基高等教育机构分类 | accessdate=2015年2月12日 | archive-date=2016年3月4日 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203655/http://carnegieclassifications.iu.edu/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=139931&start_page=institution.php&clq=%7B%22ipug2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22ipgrad2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22enrprofile2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22ugprfile2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22sizeset2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22basic2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22eng2005_ids%22:%22%22,%22search_string%22:%22georgia+southern+university%22,%22level%22:%22%22,%22control%22:%22%22,%22accred%22:%22%22,%22state%22:%22%22,%22region%22:%22%22,%22urbanicity%22:%22%22,%22womens%22:%22%22,%22hbcu%22:%22%22,%22hsi%22:%22%22,%22tribal%22:%22%22,%22msi%22:%22%22,%22landgrant%22:%22%22,%22coplac%22:%22%22,%22urban%22:%22%22%7D | dead-url=no }}</ref>，
亦被佐治亚大学系统评为综合性大学<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usg.edu/inst/group | title=大学分类 | publisher=佐治亚大学系统 | accessdate=2015年2月12日 | archive-date=2015年2月15日 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215161827/http://www.usg.edu/inst/group | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
该校提供学士，
硕士及博士学位共153个专业<ref>{{cite web | url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/georgia-southern-1572 | title=佐治亚南方大学 | publisher=美国新闻与世界报道 | accessdate=2015年2月12日 | archive-date=2011年7月20日 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720111434/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/georgia-southern-1572 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

